  %body
    .content
      %a{ href: "https://github.com/ksylvest/jquery-lighter"}
        %img.fork{ src: "images/fork.png", alt: "Fork" }
      %h1 jQuery Lighter
      %p Lighter is a jQuery plugin designed to provide gallery view for images.
      %h2 Example
      %section.examples
        .example
          %a.sample{ href:"samples/sample-01.jpg", data: { lighter: "samples/sample-01.jpg", width: '1280', height: '720' } }
            %img{ src: "samples/preview-01.jpg" }
        .example
          %a.sample{ href:"samples/sample-02.jpg", data: { lighter: "samples/sample-02.jpg", width: '1280', height: '720' } }
            %img{ src:"samples/preview-02.jpg" }
        .example
          %a.sample{ href:"samples/sample-03.jpg", data: { lighter: "samples/sample-03.jpg", width: '1280', height: '720' } }
            %img{ src:"samples/preview-03.jpg" }
        .example
          %a.sample{ href:"samples/sample-04.jpg", data: { lighter: "samples/sample-04.jpg", width: '1280', height: '720' } }
            %img{ src:"samples/preview-04.jpg" }
      %h2 Installation
      %p To install download one of these packages and include the jquery.lighter.js and jquery.lighter.css files in your head with the following:
      %section.formats
        .format
          %a.zip{ href: "packages/jquery.lighter.zip" }
        .format
          %a.tar{ href: "packages/jquery.lighter.tar" }
      %pre
        %code{ data: { language: "html" } }
          = preserve do
            :escaped
              <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.0.2/jquery.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
              <script src="javascript/jquery.lighter.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
              <link href="stylesheets/jquery.lighter.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
      %h2 Example
      %p Setting up a lighter is easy. The following snippet is a good start:
      %pre
        %code{ data: { language: "html" } }
          = preserve do
            :escaped
              <a href="samples/sample-01.jpg" data-lighter>
                <img src="samples/preview-01.jpg" />
              </a>
              <a href="samples/sample-02.jpg" data-lighter>
                <img src="samples/preview-02.jpg" />
              </a>
              <a href="samples/sample-03.jpg" data-lighter>
                <img src="samples/preview-03.jpg" />
              </a>
              <a href="samples/sample-04.jpg" data-lighter>
                <img src="samples/preview-04.jpg" />
              </a>
              <a href="samples/sample-05.jpg" data-lighter>
                <img src="samples/preview-05.jpg" />
              </a>
              <a href="samples/sample-06.jpg" data-lighter>
                <img src="samples/preview-06.jpg" />
              </a>
